osx-arm64/libktx.dylib is an unmodified binary of libktx 4.4.2 from the
Khronos Group's KTX-Software project (https://github.com/KhronosGroup/KTX-Software),
redistributed under the Apache License, Version 2.0 (see LICENSE in this
directory). It provides KTX2 container reading and Basis Universal
(BasisLZ/UASTC) transcoding for Paradise.Assets.Textures via the Ktx2.NET
binding, which ships its own natives only for win-x64 and linux-x64.

KTX-Software bundles third-party components under compatible licenses
(notably Basis Universal, Apache-2.0, Copyright 2019-2024 Binomial LLC);
see the upstream repository's LICENSES/ directory for the complete set.
